data.description: Just listed! ??Welcome to 4941 Briar Ridge Circle! This charming house offers an incredible opportunity to create your dream home. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a 2-car garage, this property is perfect for families or individuals seeking spacious living. Step inside and be greeted by beautiful new floors in the living and dining areas.  The fireplace adds warmth to the living area, creating the perfect spot for relaxation on chilly evenings. Plus, the sunroom/extra sitting area provides a versatile space for an office or playroom. The house sits on a large .41 acre lot with the back yard being fenced and a Gazebo sitting area in the front yard gives you plenty of outdoor space to enjoy.  The location of the property offers convenient access to nearby amenities such as schools, parks, shopping centers, Moody AFB, VSU, downtown Valdosta and restaurants. With its appealing features and prime location, this house presents an excellent opportunity to create lasting memories in a warm and inviting environment. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! Contact us today to schedule a viewing and make this house your new home. ????
